                     <p> Letters patent of <persName>King James I</persName>, to 
               <persName>sir <forename>John</forename> 
                           <surname>Rodney</surname>, kt.</persName>, 
               granting to him, in consideration of a payment into the exchequer of 13s. 4d.,
               the goods and chattels of <persName>
                           <forename>Barbara</forename> 
                           <surname>Buckland</surname>, late of <placeName role="person" key="place_106156">St Andrew's Holborn</placeName> and of <placeName role="person" key="place_108593">Stanelynch</placeName>
                        </persName>
