               <placeName type="manor" key="place_108728">Stanlynch, co. Wilts</placeName>, for 41 years, at an annual rent
               of 44s. 5 1/2d.
               Dated at <placeName role="date" key="place_100060">Westminster</placeName>, 6 March, <origDate notBefore="1610-03-24" notAfter="1611-03-23">8 James I</origDate>. 
